{"tid":1533346,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"國外盟友要求，快啲有英文台","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T13:26:16.000Z","uid":263094,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60829b928017f6f3a5bc7f296fd8188e8428f0ec","tid":1533346,"uid":263094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zn2ZU9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zn2ZU9.png&h=4688be43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地都想睇連登"},{"pid":"15009d7ec47264dba4d963858b1b3778de4dd224","tid":1533346,"uid":246980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:59:35.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"6d7590628d092d755bf3e8a96f79847cdcc34a9e","tid":1533346,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:00:06.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81619df9d5a9fb82a84383fd40f3ad7139c31ad8","tid":1533346,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"佢話搵專人翻譯高汁文都可行喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc2229b138eadc949aa37f6967f13d34593ecfb","tid":1533346,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:02:35.000Z","msg":"Hi m8.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> you can sign up an account with your college email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f54961634a6a271689db6f581b87ed7858f6f69","tid":1533346,"uid":201889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:02:13.000Z","msg":"開3個新台 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">- 徵求翻譯台<br />\n- English Channel [英文台]<br />\n- Other Languages Channel [外文台]</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;徵求翻譯台&quot;</span><br />\n內 Post 需要找人翻譯的文章, 最好指明想要的語言<br />\n甚至 &quot;文宣&quot; 內容也可以<br />\n在回覆內 Post 各種話言的文字翻譯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;英文台&quot; &quot;外文台&quot;</span><br />\nPost 已翻譯的文章<br />\n可能要在標題加 Tag, 分話言 e.g. [Francais] [Deutsch]"},{"pid":"e0301e36d83407fc9df5bf156e1f4082926cc28a","tid":1533346,"uid":280163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"[集思廣益] 連登必須出英文版 ！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534989</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 連登要有<span style=\"color: gold;\">翻譯台</span>+<span style=\"color: blue;\">外語台</span></span><br />\n-<span style=\"color: gold;\">翻譯台</span>：大概係一個<ins>熱門台嘅翻版</ins>，不過可以俾會員click 入去揀語言作出翻譯，<br />\n-每個翻譯都可以report，<ins>太多report唔出得街</ins><br />\n<br />\n-<span style=\"color: blue;\">外語台</span>：一個比<ins>外國人嘅介面</ins>，翻譯好嘅post會係果邊出現。<ins>以語言做大分類，以熱門程度排序。</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.開Reddit／Twitter </span><br />\n連登唔係個個外國人都識，但reddit同twitter就好多外國人用。<br />\n除咗用本土平台，<br />\n可以將<ins>今日熱門嘅post逐個總結</ins>，放上外國平台，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再係reddit／twitter link返去原本個post到。<br />\n咁樣外國人可以係佢哋平台comment俾我哋睇。</span>"},{"pid":"48780cad5b51ef809902cfba9b5c88b6d9fcf861","tid":1533346,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:15:44.000Z","msg":"你以為只有得一個user需要英文台嗎？唔信我換過其他user再send同一篇文求連登出英文台<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。<br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.幫推<br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，將入面既post再推<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.堅持每日全部post再一推<br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止"},{"pid":"ee09693b3cb16e99fc3ac4499959299ddf809e9e","tid":1533346,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}